title: Group Therapy: We Helped 6 People Today
description:
We did multiple Group Therapy's today!  

First, a listener is dating someone who spends $4,000 on a Boba Fett costume to attend Star Wars conventions and is wondering if that's a red flag.

Second, a couple is not agreeing about a baby name and doesn't know what to do. 

Third, a woman's neighbor has been flirting with another neighbor over the NextDoor app but there's a problem, the other neighbor has a partner already and has been lying about it so she wants to know if she should tell the her neighbor and/or the girlfriend.
